~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Assessing Food Safety of Polymer Packaging

A handbook by experts about the requirements for packaging foodstuffs.
http://syl.82c29.net/products_and_services/Books/Products_and_Applications/Packaging/Assessing_Food_Safety_of_Polymer_94h3avd9s.883
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Biodegradable Polymers Market Report

Customers like to see environmentally friendly products, find out who makes them and what's available.
http://syl.82c29.net/products_and_services/Books/Environment_and_Health/Biodegradation/Biodegradable_Polymers_19.883
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Food Contact Rubbers 2

Products, Migration and Regulation - a summary of a food safety research project carried out at Rapra on elastomers used in food processing.
http://syl.82c29.net/products_and_services/Books/Products_and_Applications/Packaging/Food_Contact_Rubbers_2_-_Products,_Migration_and_a7shw4q927.883
