http://syl.82c29.net/website/bookstore/special_9cfa01.883?

We are offering each of the 25 Rapra Review Reports featured in Volume 25 of the series with a 20% discount.

Rapra Review Reports provide detailed state-of-the-art reviews, combined with comprehensive bibliographic information from the Rapra Abstracts database, on wide-ranging subjects of particular interest and importance in polymer science and technology, so there is bound to be one of interest to you.
